{"tid":1718793,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"消防手足建議大量使用水魔法！！","createTime":"2019-11-14T02:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T07:21:46.000Z","uid":223623,"like":208,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f007f5d662d527c6b72f56a3e49e347d34db1a","tid":1718793,"uid":223623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:38:41.000Z","msg":"#消防投稿 <br />\n師兄你好，見你貼左呢篇文，相信有消記兄弟聯絡過你，我自己都係消記同事，想比少少意見你地，可以既安全而又達至裝修既效果<br />\n<br />\n其實係地鋪玩火，真係會危險，好容易會辣上民居，就算唔係火，齋煙都會對樓上居民有生命危險。所以我提你地不坊試下入到某d地鋪，或商場鋪。通常呢d鋪頭都有花灑頭，即係裝係天花，有個玻璃頭果d<br />\n<br />\n你地可以搵d鎖匙之類篤爆佢或者比少少熱力佢，例如火機熱爆佢。咁佢就會不斷灑水，水對於成間鋪既破壞未必會比火低，但係一定對市民，對手足安全得多，小小建議，如果你贊同請修飾下再轉達比手足們，希望你地平安，加油"},{"pid":"64bca32c61f5d289dd4d3a3bb1b29a53e624bba0","tid":1718793,"uid":337761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登嘅冷氣軍師，想幫手又冇得發夢嘅，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該幫手上Twitter，Reddit幫手！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">前線搏晒老命同班警甴對抗，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你哋唔係連撳幾個掣都懶呀嘛？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n美國議員繼續為香港發聲，大家快啲去回應支持啦～<br />\n<br />\n！！！提出法案嘅Marco Rubio話有好消息！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1194749198345949187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=83743f66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187&h=c1718001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1194749198345949187</a><br />\n<br />\n！！！Dick Durbin促請Leader McConnell 就法案進行投票！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenatorDurbin/status/1194708875972349953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorDurbin%2Fstatus%2F1194708875972349953&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=54bdf279\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorDurbin%2Fstatus%2F1194708875972349953&h=47d24cbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenatorDurbin/status/1194708875972349953</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Marsha Blackburn 繼續撐香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1194798820695138310?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1194798820695138310%3Fs%3D09&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=b639429e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1194798820695138310%3Fs%3D09&h=56d542bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1194798820695138310?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Rick Scott鬧黨媒冷血<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1194622539017752576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1194622539017752576&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=47721aaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1194622539017752576&h=2e6ec6ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1194622539017752576</a><br />\n<br />\n！！眾議院Jim McGovern話唔好各打五十大板<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1194627617913069570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1194627617913069570&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=05ce8ae9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1194627617913069570&h=c640462d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1194627617913069570</a><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">更加多嘅任務可以去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot，入\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%A5&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=a09cc92d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot，入</a> /task 做任務。<br />\nadmin團隊會持續更新任務列表。</span></span>"},{"pid":"82f19834a996a41fa7d54b80ad2289960363b8c4","tid":1718793,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:41:29.000Z","msg":"pushpushpushpushpush"},{"pid":"dbf54b04d6eec7d413ead8d48b785ab7c92c3ca4","tid":1718793,"uid":82068,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:41:50.000Z","msg":"聖水打狗<br />\n漆彈爆鋪"},{"pid":"9137af812fbde9686843b23f001f30765db2140d","tid":1718793,"uid":256505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f007f5d662d527c6b72f56a3e49e347d34db1a","tid":1718793,"uid":223623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:38:41.000Z","msg":"#消防投稿 <br />\n師兄你好，見你貼左呢篇文，相信有消記兄弟聯絡過你，我自己都係消記同事，想比少少意見你地，可以既安全而又達至裝修既效果<br />\n<br />\n其實係地鋪玩火，真係會危險，好容易會辣上民居，就算唔係火，齋煙都會對樓上居民有生命危險。所以我提你地不坊試下入到某d地鋪，或商場鋪。通常呢d鋪頭都有花灑頭，即係裝係天花，有個玻璃頭果d<br />\n<br />\n你地可以搵d鎖匙之類篤爆佢或者比少少熱力佢，例如火機熱爆佢。咁佢就會不斷灑水，水對於成間鋪既破壞未必會比火低，但係一定對市民，對手足安全得多，小小建議，如果你贊同請修飾下再轉達比手足們，希望你地平安，加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:42:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0482b70dab1daac9cd42634e21175c4d2f1c926","tid":1718793,"uid":58630,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:44:24.000Z","msg":"呢招仲要長玩長有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你燒完佢 佢起碼隔一排先裝修返好<br />\n你玩水啲貨唔要得 但過幾日又可以開返 之後無限loop<img src=\"/